{"type": "article", "id": 27722, "title": "烧水壶", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-03T06:59:03Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 42, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702163710VprHCZumFWRMLjA8.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>水壶里的水刚刚烧开，这个时候倒水总是有点心惊胆战。Fellow Design 推出的这款 Stagg 烧水壶为此特意设计了一个纤细的出水口，同时还在手柄的顶部增加了一个小平面，让你可以更精确地控制倒水的过程。不仅实用，造型也非常优雅。你还可以通过壶盖上的温度计实时掌控温度。这是它的<a href=\"https://fancy.com/things/1160074961885332359/Stagg-Pour-Over-Kettle\">购买链接</a>，售价为 69 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163708MCc4r5FW2XztxDI3.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.76190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021637085uQkqRBKIA1lx4ip.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163709FORyZWp3gXzs4lH0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163709lMpPICoaA4egW8Km.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.52407407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}